  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Linder is a very welcoming hotel in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva</a>, where you’ll find an array of shops, bars and restaurants. The famous Ciampioni lift is just 50 metres away so you’ll also be perfectly placed to enjoy the many activities available in the surrounding area, including the hiking and cycling trails that remain ever popular with visitors.</p>
<p>This comfortable property is loving run by the Linder Family who will personally ensure you have a good stay. The hotel’s mix of traditional and modern give it a homely feel, and cosy guest rooms are a welcoming retreat after a busy day. The lovely restaurant serves up excellent cuisine for dinner, using influences from South Tyrol and <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a> to create a fresh menu with local produce. Those wanting to relax can use the spa facilities at the nearby Hotel Nives where you’ll find an indoor pool and a choice of saunas.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 2 hours 30 mins by coach.</p>]]></description>
