  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p>The Alpine dining room at Hotel Linder is a great spot for a wonderful evening meal. Enjoy delicious South Tyrolean and Italian cuisine that’s been made using fresh, local ingredients. The cosy bar is the perfect place for a pre-dinner drink or to relax after your meal.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Wellness</strong></span></p>
<p>Guests of the hotel can use the facilities at the nearby Hotel Nives. The spa area offers an indoor pool and saunas. A range of massages are also available to book locally (payable locally). Children aged 14 years and under are welcome to use the spa until 4pm.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Health suite with fitness room and sauna</li>
<li>Whirlpool (payable locally)</li>
<li>Small garden and terrace area</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
